# Voice to Text Converter (Real-Time)

A simple and efficient **real-time voice-to-text converter** built using:

- Python  
- FastAPI  
- OpenAI Realtime API  
- Streamlit (optional UI)  
- Microphone Audio Recorder  

This project listens to your voice and converts it to text in **real time**, similar to how Alexa/Google Assistant work.

